# UMKM Cepat Design AMD

## Reference read
Reference: lovable.dev. Use as aesthetic reference, not a direct clone. Do not copy proprietary assets, copy, logo, exact DOM, or hosted fonts without license.

Observed direction:
- Huge centered headline.
- Very sparse hero.
- Light canvas.
- Product composer/input as the main UI metaphor.
- Minimal chrome.
- Below hero: company/template/proof areas with lots of whitespace.
- Few visible icons. Avoid icon confetti.

## Current design decision
Closer to Lovable essence while correcting earlier plainness:
- Light page only.
- No decorative gradient blobs.
- No rocket logo in landing shell.
- No generic AI pills.
- No three-icon-card AI-slop section.
- Typography carries the page.
- Hero composer includes a compact preview pane so it feels product-led, not like a static textarea.
- Template cards use intentional mini landing-page compositions, not empty skeleton placeholders.
- Lower sections use varied layout rhythm instead of repeated card blocks.

## Tokens
- Background: `#f7f7f3`
- Surface: `#ffffff`
- Soft surface: `#fbfbf8`
- Ink: `#111111`
- Muted: `rgba(17,17,17,.56)`
- Subtle muted: `rgba(17,17,17,.42)`
- Border: `rgba(17,17,17,.10-.12)`
- Accent: `#ff5a3d`
- Accent dark: `#e6452d`
- Radius: composer/cards `28px`, inner panels `18-22px`, controls `14px`, nav CTA `999px`
- Shadow: soft neutral only, no colored glow

## Typography
- Use existing sans stack for licensing safety.
- Lovable uses a custom Camera variable font; do not vendor it unless licensed.
- Match feeling through scale, tracking, whitespace.
- H1: very large, tight, max 2 lines desktop where possible.
- Body: short. No long explainers in hero.

## Layout
1. Header: text wordmark only, center nav, right CTA/account links.
2. Hero: centered headline, one subtext, two-pane composer with prompt + generated preview.
3. Logo/trust strip: simple muted text marks, no icons.
4. Template grid: six mini page previews with business-specific labels and distinct information density.
5. How it works: split editorial heading + three numbered process columns.
6. Open source: quiet final band with provider credibility and GitHub link.
7. Footer: quiet text/nav links.

## Copy
- Indonesian.
- Direct, product-led.
- Avoid buzzwords and dense provider wording above fold.
- No fake metrics.

## Explicit bans
- No rocket logo in header/footer/hero.
- No background gradient blobs.
- No icon cards.
- No generic pills scattered through page.
- No dark section flip.
- No em dashes.
- No fake precise metrics.
- No dummy skeleton-only cards.

## Quality gate
- `lint`, `typecheck`, `test`, `build` pass.
- ABK inspect/review passes.
- Desktop, mobile, and fullpage screenshots manually reviewed.
- Console/network clean for landing page.
